Description: Simple UFW GUI for Goldendog Linux
 A GTK4/libadwaita interface for configuring UFW firewall defaults
 and rules with a simplified workflow.
 .
 Features:
  - Toggle firewall state and default inbound/outbound policy
  - Add/edit/remove simple and advanced UFW rules
  - Privileged apply via pkexec helper
  - Multi-language support
